_sText:
If you want it done right, do it yourself.

That's pretty much what I went by when designing the _perfect_ Gun Game map. Testing it was great, the map is very fun and literally perfect for gun game. Lots of good coverage, an underground short-cut, some paths that will lead to enemies popping up and surprising you, some direct paths, it's overall really fun.

I hope you enjoy this piece of art, and would be honored to see it on a server.

Also this map is recommended to have the color saturation on your monitor all the way up, it's so awesome.
